overview:
Monet Minerals is a home-based business that offers all-natural mineral makeup.

Founded in 2006 Monet Minerals is located in North St. Paul, MN.

Currently we have over 200 consultants across the Country and serve clients in every state.

Our Mission at Monet Minerals is to provide a natural product at an inexpensive price while helping others earn extra income using our popular Mineral Consultant Program.Products:Our product line includes mineral foundations, eye shadows, blushes and MVPs (multi-versatile powders that can be used on eyes, lips, cheeks and nails). We also have lip balm and our skin care line.
